author: The Babylon Bee
description:
Corporal Wade Miller landed on the beaches of Normandy during the early morning hours of June 6, 1944. But now, he's calling the military out for only sending cisgendered males to the fight.

Watch the full video: https://youtu.be/CnSe35Wd7p0

title: WW2 Vet Horrified By Lack Of Trans Representation On D-Day
